This environement builder is tested with Centos 6.1 and 6.5

Make sure that package ruby and febootstrap are installed.

yum install -y febootstrap ruby 

Make sure that you are connected to the internet.
If you using proxy export http_proxy=ip.proxy:3128 to avoid resolution problems.

When you are ready type : make all.

The script build vmlinuz and initrd.
